## Development

### Setup

```bash
# Install development dependencies
uv sync --dev

# Install pre-commit hooks
uv run pre-commit install
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run all tests
uv run pytest

# Run with coverage
uv run pytest --cov

# Run specific test types
uv run pytest -m unit
uv run pytest -m integration
uv run pytest -m e2e
```

